      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "PUBLIC (signed URL access):\nresources :deals (show)\n \u251c resources :documents\n \u2502  \u2514 resource :requirement\n \u2514 resources :requirements\n    \u2514 POST submit_all\n\nWEBHOOKS:\nresource :ocrolus (create)\n\nOAUTH:\nGET auth/google_oauth2/callback\nGET auth/failure\n\nroot \u2192 redirect#index\nGET up \u2192 health_check\nGET home/dashboard",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
